&lt;h2 id="1-data-controller"&gt;1. Data Controller&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marco Baccarani&lt;/strong&gt; (Committa) — &lt;a href="https://committa.it/en/contatti/"&gt;Contact form&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-processed-data-and-third-party-services"&gt;2. Processed data and third-party services&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a static website: it does not collect or store personal data directly. Data is processed exclusively by the following third-party services:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="21-github-pages-hosting"&gt;2.1 GitHub Pages (hosting)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The website is hosted on GitHub Pages (GitHub, Inc.). Visiting the site involves the automatic collection of technical browsing data (e.g., IP address) by GitHub, necessary for service delivery. The Data Controller does not have access to these logs nor uses them.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>